== Old Age ==
Most of the time relationships will die because their time expired, or by diseases they have. These deaths are the most common and can happen anytime over 65.

== Terrorist attacks ==
If your character lives in [[Iraq]], [[Afghanistan]], [[Syria]], [[Pakistan]], or [[Venezuela]]; the character's family, lovers, or friends could suddenly die from terrorist or battlefield attacks. Starting with the February 2020 update however, family members can die from terrorist attacks in countries other than the ones shown above, the player is mostly exempt from these however.<gallery>
